@0    = ~I can't stay with this group any longer. I have to call it quits.~
@1    = ~Ah well, even the best things pass away.  Your company was enjoyable while it lasted.  Perhaps we shall meet again.~
@2    = ~Coran, I erred. Please, do not leave.~
@3    = ~Wait for us in Athkatla, near the city gates. We will come for you later.~
@4    = ~Just wait for me here.~
@5    = ~It seems we have crossed paths yet again.  Shall we renew our partnership and travel together?~
@6    = ~Of course! Join me, and let the Lady Luck smile on us both!~
@7    = ~Not now, Coran.~
@8    = ~Ah, old friends made new again.  A pairing that cannot be beaten.~
@9    = ~Ahhh, perhaps another time. Come back if you change your mind.~